<p>My visual brainstorm, crafting the personality of an artist who loves tech.</p>
{% endcall %} {% call section("STYLE GUIDE", "/assets/fabric-imgs/fabric-style-guide.png") %}
<p>
  A soft lavender with a light yellow conveys creativity and warmth. Paired with cartoony icons and
  bubbly fonts, I hope to support an artsy, inclusive, and gentle aesthetic. The name
  <b>FABRIC</b> refers to both a material of woven fibers —each artwork intertwined on one central
  platform— and to the fabric of time, reflecting how artwork is timeless, living, and always
  influential.
</p>
